content.rendered:
Directed by Sanjay Leela Bhansali

Written by Sanjay Leela Bhansali. Abhiruchi Chand. Saurabh H. Dikshit. Prakash Kapadia. Mitakshara Kumar. Karan Singh Rathore. Utkarshini Vashishtha. Utkarshini Vashishtha

Star Alia Bhatt (Gangubai Kathiawadi). Shantanu Maheshwari (Afsaan). Vijay Raaz (Raziabai). Indira Tiwari (Kamli). Seema Pahwa (Sheila Masi (as Seema Bhargava)). Varun Kapoor (Ramnik). Jim Sarbh (Amin Faizl). Ajay Devgn (Rahim Lala). Aakash Pandey (Munna)

Language Hindi. Telugu

Producers Sanjay Leela Bhansali. Jayantilal Gada. Arvinder Gill. Jaspinder Kang. Pratik Rawal. Vikram Yadav

Production Bhansali Productions. Pen Studios
